  "title": "System Analyst",
  "description": "<h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>4 years of relevant working experience</strong> in system analysis, application development, and support.</p></li><li><p>Strong hands-on experience in <strong>Java application development</strong>, including:</p><ul><li><p>Core Java, OOP concepts, collections, multithreading, and exception handling</p></li><li><p>Java-based enterprise frameworks such as <strong>Spring / Spring Boot</strong></p></li><li><p>RESTful web services and API integration</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Experience with <strong>Java application deployment</strong> in containerized environments using <strong>Docker</strong> and <strong>Kubernetes</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Working experience with databases using <strong>SQL</strong> and <strong>Oracle</strong>, including performance tuning and query optimization.</p></li><li><p>Experience with additional programming languages and technologies such as <strong>JavaScript, GoLang, C#, and Solidity</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Experience in <strong>iOS and Android mobile application</strong> environments.</p></li><li><p>Experience working with <strong>container frameworks</strong> and modern microservices-based architectures.</p></li><li><p>Exposure to <strong>POS systems and/or Blockchain technologies</strong> is an advantage.</p></li><li><p>Strong analytical, troubleshooting, and technical documentation skills.</p></li><li><p>Willingness to provide <strong>24/7 on-call support</strong>,</p></li></ul>",
